  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/3339cffd1a9df1e2946175471a5f5c1c.avif?t=1666088725\" width=610 height=278 /></span><br>Gray Bone fights for peace in the beautiful universe of the Gray Orange World!<br><br>Some of the creatures were covered with red skin and became hostile and aggressive, the most dangerous creatures can shock and do not let anyone into their territory. In the Gray-orange world, there is very little habitable land, and it is all divided into islands, the main character will have to destroy all the hostile creatures and solve all the puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/8e3001eaf6ab046895e9e7955b2194bb.poster.avif?t=1666088725\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/8e3001eaf6ab046895e9e7955b2194bb.webm?t=1666088725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/8e3001eaf6ab046895e9e7955b2194bb.mp4?t=1666088725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features of the game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A lot of jumping and moving in the horizontal and vertical direction<br></li><li>Endless rounds of ammunition<br></li><li>Teleports TVs and doors!<br></li><li>Levers and switches.<br></li><li>Dangerous opponents throw thorns, electrocute and shoot.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/d6112c76e31b0d73e132956036264ba9.poster.avif?t=1666088725\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/d6112c76e31b0d73e132956036264ba9.webm?t=1666088725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559960/extras/d6112c76e31b0d73e132956036264ba9.mp4?t=1666088725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
